---
title: Mexican Beef & Black Bean Chilli with Cheddar Cheese & Corn Salsa
description: Put your own stamp on this Mexican-style beef and black bean chilli by customising the spice level to suit your tastes. Pair it with an easy corn and tomato salsa, sour cream and lemon for a meal that's made to please.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d5cc61e4da29b00085776ba-36db4978.jpg
